  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/50px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/75px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/100px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Maldon IV Durrandon</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/50px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/75px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/100px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nMaldon IV Durrandon</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Storm King</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Heir</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Durran_XXIV_Durrandon\" title=\"Durran XXIV Durrandon\">Durran XXIV Durrandon</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Successor</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Durran_XXIV_Durrandon\" title=\"Durran XXIV Durrandon\">Durran XXIV Durrandon</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Queen</th><td>\nAndal wife</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Durran_XXIV_Durrandon\" title=\"Durran XXIV Durrandon\">Durran XXIV Durrandon</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Maldon IV Durrandon</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Storm King</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maldon_IV_Durrandon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal_invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal invasion\">Andal invasion</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a>, as neither side defeated the other, Maldon took an <a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a> maiden as his wife. <a href=\"/index.php/Durran_XXIV_Durrandon\" title=\"Durran XXIV Durrandon\">Durran XXIV</a> was born of this union.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafandals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafandals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maldon_IV_Durrandon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafandals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafandals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Andals in the Stormlands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404194034\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.104 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.408 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 535/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 11031/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6793/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 582/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 617/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.290/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.47 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  392.269      1 -total\n 97.64%  383.004      1 Template:Infobox_monarch\n 96.79%  379.672      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.44%   40.959     14 Template:Infobox_value\n  5.26%   20.626      5 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.77%    6.948 